    "Furthermore, preprint review services, preprint servers, and indexing and • Consider preprints and their reviews in evaluations for funding, hiring, degree requirements, fellowship eligibility, tenure, and promotion.",
    "Make this consideration explicit on your website and in application instructions, for example, by adopting a CV format that enables listing preprints and their reviews (where the candidate is an author of a preprint) and reviews of preprints (where the candidate is a preprint reviewer).",
